name: Zugaikotsu no Fuhai
description: Zugaikotsu is a vengeful spirit.  She is believed to be the youngest child of a poor family living in a village 2000 years ago.  She made a deal with some demons and returned to take revenge on a shogun who ordered his family to be killed. Rots the heads of her victims to kill in the most painful way. She is seen very rarely and appears to instil the vengeance  of other demons and to teach torture methods.
